          "Missing prerequisites",
          "Disk storage is full",
          "Network interruption"
        ]
      },
      {
        "title": "Troubleshooting",
        "content": [
          "Run the installer as Administrator.",
          "Verify available disk space.",
          "Download the installer again if corrupted.",
          "Temporarily disable antivirus if approved by IT.",
          "Install all required dependencies.",
          "Restart the computer after installation.",
          "Contact IT Support if installation continues to fail."
        ]
      },
      {
        "title": "Best Practices",
        "content": [
          "Install software only from approved sources.",
          "Keep applications updated.",
          "Avoid installing unauthorized software.",
          "Always verify software licenses.",
          "Restart the device after major installations."
        ]
      },
      {
        "title": "FAQ",
        "content": [
          {
            "question": "The installation failed. What should I do?",
            "answer": "Run the installer as Administrator and verify that all prerequisites are installed."
          },
          {
            "question": "The application crashes after opening.",
            "answer": "Update the application and reinstall it if necessary."
          },
          {
            "question": "The license cannot be activated.",
            "answer": "Verify your license key or contact the IT Administrator."
          }
        ]
